{"tid":906898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸客遊台北側側膊走數 笑稱：3天食肉到怕","createTime":"2018-11-18T11:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T13:37:35.000Z","uid":201464,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6926701c94889b21e16ba22cff2e7cc1e64ba6","tid":906898,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181118/58927676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927676&d=NmIsk%2FOHFY55l6IH0G3W0kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=1384a215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927676&h=f3adc9b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181118/58927676</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542515496_a528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542515496_a528.jpg&h=9012835b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到台旅遊竟吃霸王餐，還是一時大意？！12名大陸遊客前晚約7時許到台北大安區一間火鍋店用餐，加上服務費，一共9,229元新台幣（下同，約2,348港元）。一行人飽足後在店門口聊天，然後一一離開，但沒有任何人結帳，店家因晚餐時間忙碌也沒發現，事後才驚覺「怎麼人都消失了！」緊急向警方報案。店長說，這群陸客或許不是故意吃霸王餐，希望他們看到報道後，能前來買單。 <br />\n<br />\n據火鍋店鄭姓店長說，陸客沒有事先訂位，臨時來店裏用餐，當晚約7時許陸續有8人到場，店家安排他們坐在獨立包廂，他們把招牌的肉品都點了一輪。閉路電視拍下，當晚8個人吃過一輪後，三三兩兩走到門外抽煙、閒聊，有些人就沒有再回來。到晚間8時許，又有4名女子到場，坐在同一個包廂用餐。他們一行12人（共6男、6女）約在9時許全數離去。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據當晚送餐的火鍋店服務生表示，他們操着類似地方方言的口音，聽不出來是哪裏人，依稀聽見陸客閒聊，「來台灣3天都在吃肉，真的吃到好怕」，也有人討論台灣的化妝用品，看起來就像一般來台觀光的旅行團。火鍋店負責人指，陸客離開前，有一名綠衣女子進到店內，疑似告知他們接下來的行程，就帶着在包廂內用餐的4女離去，一夥人還在店門口閒聊幾句才慢慢走到路口，隨後就全部離開，沒人出面付帳。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，該批陸客點了牛小排、雪花牛、羊肩等肉品，另外還有火鍋料、滷味等，加上服務費，一共9,229元。鄭姓店長認為，客人或許不是故意吃霸王餐，也許是每個人都以為同行間有人已經結帳，才會吃完就離開，但是店家仍先向警方報案，轄區派出所則表示已翻看閉路電視，釐清該群陸客去向。"},{"pid":"e58ea1d89d8a8a1543295f631f3a38ecb3419b95","tid":906898,"uid":35014,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f1eebebaa1d450ad103cd65d3823a12ed30dc6d","tid":906898,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"唔係故意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df21439f7dcc1ce9e2a14bef094b762f3c9ec24","tid":906898,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"要不是&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"a85103d02602ce75666660f8c74fc37a457fd81d","tid":906898,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c13d7a3a29c56918e725607614f28a3ee39916e","tid":906898,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"個店長本身係支那人？<br />\n咁天真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e74e9da18a1caa78879d36ffc734e34a0b6353","tid":906898,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37ed62e6d1865fa33ff971a27d9b387c9688186","tid":906898,"uid":21545,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4c13d7a3a29c56918e725607614f28a3ee39916e","tid":906898,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"個店長本身係支那人？<br />\n咁天真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"就係台灣人先咁天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40089e570c2d26c4a6b87c1679efe